OL,3,CWeek-long illegal working crackdown
OL,4,Csees 75 detained
OL,6,FImmigration Enforcement officers have
OL,7,Fdetained 75 suspected illegal workers
OL,8,Fas part of a week-long crackdown.
OL,10,FOfficers visited more than 225
OL,11,Fbusinesses in the past week,
OL,12,Fparticularly car washes, with 122
OL,13,Freceiving civil penalties for
OL,14,Femploying illegal workers, the Home
OL,15,FOffice said.
