OL,6,FYvette Cooper, the Home Secretary,
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is completely wrong that
OL,8,Fdodgy employers can work hand-in-glove
OL,9,Fwith the smuggling gangs who risk
OL,10,Fpeople's lives to bring them here
OL,11,Fillegally and push them into off-the-
OL,12,Fbooks employment.
OL,14,F"These workers are sold complete lies
OL,15,Fby the gangs before being made to live
OL,16,Fand work in appalling conditions for a
OL,17,Fpittance. We are determined to put a
OL,18,Fstop to this, which is exactly why we
OL,19,Fhave launched crackdowns such as this.
