OL,6,F"While this operation marks an
OL,7,Fimportant step forward, our commitment
OL,8,Fto tackling this issue is ongoing. We
OL,9,Fwill ensure those who break the rules
OL,10,Fface the full force of the law."
OL,12,FOfficials said illegal workers were
OL,13,Foften kept in "squalid" conditions,
OL,14,Fpaid below the minimum wage and forced
OL,15,Fto work long hours, while their
OL,16,Femployers undercut their competitors
OL,17,Fand often did not pay their fair share
OL,18,Fof taxes.
