OL,6,FBusinesses found to be employing
OL,7,Fpeople illegally face fines of up to
OL,8,F#45,000 per worker for the first
OL,9,Foffence and up to #60,000 per worker
OL,10,Ffor repeat offenders.
OL,12,FMs Cooper announced plans for
OL,13,FImmigration Enforcement to "intensify"
OL,14,Foperations over the summer shortly
OL,15,Fafter coming to office in July as part
OL,16,Fof Labour's plans to improve border
OL,17,Fsecurity.
