OL,6,FOn Wednesday, she said she wanted to
OL,7,Fuse the next six months to achieve the
OL,8,Fhighest rate of removals since 2018 of
OL,9,Fpeople with no right to be in the UK
OL,10,Fand announced a new "intelligence-
OL,11,Fdriven" plan to tackle businesses
OL,12,Femploying people illegally.
OL,14,FEddy Montgomery, director of
OL,15,Fenforcement, compliance and crime at
OL,16,FImmigration Enforcement, said: "This
OL,17,Fweek's operation shows how dedicated
OL,18,Fthe Home Office is to protecting
OL,19,Fvulnerable people and holding
OL,20,Femployers accountable.
